{"id":"08a6dd2f-fcd8-45ae-bbb5-26898d95841d","title":"1549/03/15: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"d884e629-aea0-4c95-8c6b-de89d9859cdb","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, March 15th, 1549.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c0e1fd7e-27ba-462b-81d8-949818a486eb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f04771f7-b008-47ad-9218-68ba94a89a51","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"18d9c5a4-eba7-449a-8c56-97719e89856f","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":26,"value":"d85a4e57-398b-4556-a9d0-78797a485f28","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"20545731-5a6b-4579-aec9-b9a4f360e15d","type":"style/superscript","start":19,"end":20,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c23ded4f-d7fe-4026-a4d9-d49133a47aa8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2135208f-83fa-4fc4-a0e6-718b36b6a364","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dc2641b2-550d-49f2-9873-3cf13220a2a8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7fb85d1b-a426-464f-9626-d01bc616cb73","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d1a392ba-dcd7-477c-a4ed-0018b69da3cb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a119e387-ac00-4215-bda4-3d5c031a4317","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"475405bc-ed5d-4363-bbe8-0c47d8788ff6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f9096254-6397-4bce-ad49-ab5c36be7898","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I need not tell thee over again what I have already said in my last letter. As to this dysuria I am suffering from, I have since been very ill on account of it, groaning in pain night and day without sleep and without respite of any kind. According to what the doctors say, they think I am suffering from calculus. As yet they are not sure, but in the meantime I am being treated for that complaint and am encouraged to be hopeful about the result. Nevertheless, old as I am and suffering from so cruel a malady, I must not be too sanguine about their effecting a cure. I have been advised to try the Baths at Viterbo, but it will be impossible to go there until the beginning of May: meanwhile I am filling in the time as best I may, and perhaps I shall be fortunate enough to find the trouble grow less, or to find a good remedy for it. I have much need of God\u0027s assistance at the moment. Tell Francesca, therefore, to intercede for me; and tell her that if she could know how ill I have been she would readily discover that she is not without companions in trouble. In all other respects I am pretty much as I was at thirty years. This illness has\u00A0crept upon me as the result of incessant discomfort and continued neglect of my health. Patience!\u00A0Perhaps it will turn out better than I suppose, with\u00A0God\u0027s help: and if it end otherwise I will let thee know about it. Unless I write to thee myself do not be disturbed by anything thou mayst hear from others. If I am suffering from calculus the doctors tell me the disease is in a very early stage and\u00A0therefore a small matter; and for this reason, as I\u00A0have already said, they are very hopeful about it.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"840fe2a2-52e4-44b5-8846-968a8b91f018","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":fals